WEBVTT

00:00.024 --> 00:04.972
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

00:05.944 --> 00:08.652
♪ My heart is racing ♪

00:09.784 --> 00:13.792
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

00:13.816 --> 00:18.572
♪ Hey, when I imagine you ♪

00:19.608 --> 00:22.636
♪ What kind of look ♪

00:23.640 --> 00:27.584
♪ Attracted me to you ♪

00:27.608 --> 00:30.880
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:30.904 --> 00:34.368
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:34.392 --> 00:39.640
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:39.640 --> 00:41.258
♪ I love you ♪

00:41.258 --> 00:44.736
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:44.760 --> 00:48.032
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:48.056 --> 00:53.728
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:53.752 --> 00:55.096
♪ I love you ♪

00:55.096 --> 00:58.432
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:58.456 --> 01:01.804
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:01.912 --> 01:07.109
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:07.109 --> 01:08.792
♪ I love you ♪

01:08.792 --> 01:12.192
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

01:12.216 --> 01:15.616
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:15.640 --> 01:21.216
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:21.240 --> 01:24.652
♪ I love you ♪

01:26.930 --> 01:27.720
=Love Me, Love My Voice=

01:27.720 --> 01:30.600
=Love Me, Love My Voice=
=Episode 3=

01:30.600 --> 01:34.332
(Sheng, do you owe me something?)

01:35.048 --> 01:38.153
It's not about popularity.
It's about capability.

01:38.653 --> 01:41.813
Yeah, hasn't everyone
started from the ground up?

01:41.813 --> 01:44.813
You try it. It's just
a pre-release anyway.

01:44.813 --> 01:46.373
A gift given back to the fans.

01:46.373 --> 01:47.873
Take it easy.

01:53.412 --> 01:55.832
Okay, I'll try.

01:56.612 --> 01:59.432
They're all my favorite singers.

01:59.432 --> 02:02.344
I never dreamed of being able
to collaborate with them.

02:02.344 --> 02:04.072
I'll give it my all.

02:05.852 --> 02:09.972
Only Shengshengman is brave enough
to consider a lineup like this.

02:09.972 --> 02:12.893
Only Qiang Qingci can

02:12.893 --> 02:15.132
invite so many people.

02:15.132 --> 02:17.032
We haven't collaborated for a long time.

02:17.613 --> 02:20.200
It's quite interesting

02:20.200 --> 02:21.752
to gather together sometimes.

02:23.132 --> 02:24.273
Grandpa.

02:25.132 --> 02:26.813
Don't you watch the CCTV Gala?

02:26.813 --> 02:28.813
I've watched it all on Weibo.

02:28.813 --> 02:32.072
It's the Spring Festival.
You won't chat with us?

02:32.692 --> 02:35.512
I'm talking with a few friends
about work.

02:36.173 --> 02:37.352
Dad.

02:38.173 --> 02:39.532
You're here.

02:39.532 --> 02:41.773
Sheng, they're about to leave.
Go downstairs.

02:41.773 --> 02:42.773
Right, see them out.

02:42.773 --> 02:43.373
Together.

02:43.373 --> 02:44.333
Okay.

02:44.333 --> 02:46.433
(Admin Shengshengman: Excuse me.)

02:47.972 --> 02:49.833
Shengshengman is offline?

02:51.132 --> 02:54.153
It is Lunar New Year's Eve after all.
Family time.

02:55.173 --> 02:58.313
Mr. Mo, can I be considered
part of your family?

03:00.093 --> 03:02.252
You flatter me. But it's heartwarming.

03:02.252 --> 03:04.093
I made dinner. Would you like some?

03:04.093 --> 03:05.713
No need. Thanks.

03:06.653 --> 03:07.493
I'll go back.

03:07.493 --> 03:09.653
You're wearing so little. It's cold.

03:09.653 --> 03:10.813
You should wear a coat.

03:10.813 --> 03:12.412
I'll be back shortly.

03:12.972 --> 03:15.213
Uncle, Auntie,
you don't need to see me off.

03:15.213 --> 03:17.333
It's cold, and Grandpa is at home alone.

03:17.333 --> 03:18.773
We'll walk you a bit more.

03:18.773 --> 03:20.252
How about this?

03:20.252 --> 03:21.613
You and Sheng go back.

03:21.613 --> 03:23.673
I'll see them off.

03:24.373 --> 03:27.412
Okay then. Come to visit another day.

03:27.412 --> 03:28.093
Bye.

03:28.093 --> 03:29.372
- Bye.
- Bye.

03:29.896 --> 03:31.412
We're leaving.

03:31.412 --> 03:32.173
Come again.

03:32.173 --> 03:32.852
Okay.

03:32.852 --> 03:34.632
Just hurry back.

03:35.452 --> 03:37.132
What are you doing?

03:37.132 --> 03:37.373
Mom.

03:37.373 --> 03:39.252
You've been restless all night.

03:39.252 --> 03:40.653
I just went offline hastily.

03:40.653 --> 03:42.373
I'm afraid they'd misunderstood.

03:42.373 --> 03:43.532
Misunderstood what?

03:43.532 --> 03:46.373
It's nearly midnight.
People should be asleep.

03:46.373 --> 03:49.053
Mom, I must hurry.
They tend to sleep late.

03:49.053 --> 03:49.452
You.

03:49.452 --> 03:51.472
Please be online.

03:56.140 --> 03:56.933
(Doudoubing)

03:56.933 --> 03:58.273
Mr. Qiang.

03:59.132 --> 04:00.053
I'm here.

04:00.053 --> 04:02.752
Why don't you
put on a little show for us?

04:03.333 --> 04:04.393
Sure.

04:04.973 --> 04:06.012
Sheng is back.

04:06.012 --> 04:07.652
Let's go to the public chatroom.

04:07.652 --> 04:08.752
Okay.

04:12.236 --> 04:13.884
(Perfect Voice Chatroom)

04:15.053 --> 04:19.452
Everyone, Mr. Qiang has prepared
some gifts for the festival.

04:19.452 --> 04:20.853
What kind of gifts?

04:20.853 --> 04:21.768
(Here he is. What's it?)

04:21.768 --> 04:22.632
(It's not usual.)

04:22.632 --> 04:23.240
(Legal?)

04:23.240 --> 04:24.332
(The recorder is on.)

04:24.332 --> 04:27.484
(Can you record a wake-up ringtone?)
Feishao, what took you so long?

04:27.613 --> 04:29.392
(Feishao)
Wait. Coming.

04:30.332 --> 04:32.204
(Happy New Year)
Excuse me. You eat.

04:32.204 --> 04:34.176
(Qianli Room)

04:37.813 --> 04:40.152
What kind of show would be good?

04:40.813 --> 04:41.853
Is singing good?

04:41.853 --> 04:43.473
- Singing?
- Singing?

04:45.733 --> 04:47.793
Sheng, add the subtitles.

04:51.533 --> 04:53.853
I type slowly,
and I haven't done it before.

04:53.853 --> 04:56.313
I'm afraid I can't keep up with you.

04:58.053 --> 05:00.168
It doesn't matter. Just feel free.

05:00.168 --> 05:02.072
(Can I really be casual?)

05:03.892 --> 05:08.433
Okay, what do you want to sing?
Let me search the lyrics.

05:13.413 --> 05:15.072
Bones to Sand.

05:20.684 --> 05:23.260
(SoSearch, Lyrics of Bones to Sand)

05:25.068 --> 05:26.620
(Teleprompter)

05:38.413 --> 05:40.293
♪ I traveled all over the world ♪

05:40.293 --> 05:44.156
♪ I trod through the ocean
of flowers and mountains ♪

05:45.012 --> 05:47.173
♪ Looking back,
the best years have gone by ♪

05:47.173 --> 05:52.328
♪ Who can bear to hear
the dreary sound of a Qiang flute ♪

05:52.328 --> 05:53.733
(Qiang Qingci)

05:53.733 --> 05:55.293
♪ I poured the wine skyward ♪

05:55.293 --> 06:00.053
♪ It can't quench
the everlasting flames of war ♪

06:00.053 --> 06:02.533
♪ I laugh, knowing even
my glorious achievements ♪

06:02.533 --> 06:06.913
♪ Cannot withstand the burial of time ♪

06:08.652 --> 06:10.293
♪ Clouds and moon accompany me ♪

06:10.293 --> 06:12.613
♪ I ride a horse back into the desert ♪

06:12.613 --> 06:14.092
♪ A long spear pokes through ♪

06:14.092 --> 06:16.572
♪ What does fate matter ♪

06:16.572 --> 06:17.892
♪ If love and hatred can't be avoided ♪

06:17.892 --> 06:22.892
♪ Under the flying sand lie the bones ♪

06:22.892 --> 06:25.373
♪ I am destined
to be a bloodthirsty warrior ♪

06:25.373 --> 06:27.493
♪ Only one survives in victory ♪

06:27.493 --> 06:30.692
♪ Raise my eyebrows
and sweep away all doubts ♪

06:30.692 --> 06:33.092
♪ It's worth my youth's love
for hardships ♪

06:33.092 --> 06:35.132
♪ I am invincible and lonely ♪

06:35.132 --> 06:38.533
♪ Who can outshine me ♪

06:38.533 --> 06:42.252
♪ Ancient landscapes feel like
it was just yesterday ♪

06:42.252 --> 06:46.493
♪ Who has passed by in this dream ♪

06:46.493 --> 06:48.332
♪ This tarnished iron armor ♪

06:48.332 --> 06:53.392
♪ Has been hidden in legends ♪

06:55.572 --> 06:57.632
♪ Wars spanning vast distances ♪

06:58.293 --> 07:00.152
♪ Bones to sand ♪

07:01.212 --> 07:02.952
♪ Homeland ♪

07:04.053 --> 07:05.340
♪ Remains unburied ♪

07:05.973 --> 07:07.933
♪ Snow over mountains ♪

07:07.933 --> 07:09.660
♪ Slaughtered and empty ♪

07:11.733 --> 07:13.724
♪ I turn around ♪

07:14.293 --> 07:18.072
♪ But no one returns ♪

07:24.293 --> 07:27.212
(Feishao)
I think I can quit singing.

07:27.212 --> 07:29.332
Don't even call him
Qiang Qingci anymore.

07:29.332 --> 07:31.493
Just call him the Singing God.

07:31.493 --> 07:36.072
Really, bros. You should
hear the live version. It's superb.

07:36.813 --> 07:38.373
Let's stop here.

07:38.373 --> 07:41.092
So cruel. You're keeping us in suspense.

07:41.092 --> 07:42.733
This is infuriating.

07:42.733 --> 07:45.033
Don't you guys know Qiang Qingci?

07:45.533 --> 07:49.173
How about I sing
a nursery rhyme for you all?

07:49.173 --> 07:52.092
Get lost. So many good singers
are here tonight.

07:52.092 --> 07:53.053
You keep quiet.

07:53.053 --> 07:54.892
Right. I haven't even started yet.

07:54.892 --> 07:55.813
I haven't, either.

07:55.813 --> 07:57.813
Fine, should I just mute the mic?

07:57.813 --> 07:59.720
Mr. Qiang,

07:59.720 --> 08:03.853
(Doudoubing)
anything to say to your fans or us?

08:03.853 --> 08:07.113
Any New Year wishes?
It's almost midnight countdown.

08:08.813 --> 08:10.072
Let me think.

08:19.368 --> 08:22.140
(Have a great new year. Love you forever.)
(Love you. Glad to meet you.)

08:23.053 --> 08:24.872
I want to tell you.

08:26.492 --> 08:28.553
Don't be infatuated
with a person too much

08:29.212 --> 08:31.393
because of their voice.

08:33.212 --> 08:35.572
You will never know

08:35.572 --> 08:39.472
who the voice
on the other end belongs to,

08:40.253 --> 08:41.352
right?

08:45.492 --> 08:49.013
(Juemei Shayi)
It's okay to like just the voice.

08:49.013 --> 08:51.893
Be rational.

08:51.893 --> 08:54.673
Never get deceived because of the voice.

08:55.332 --> 08:56.956
Kids, step aside.

08:57.492 --> 09:00.832
It's Chinese New Year.
Come and set off some fireworks.

09:02.253 --> 09:03.513
Come on.

09:04.212 --> 09:07.133
The Perfect Voice Studio
wishes you all a happy New Year.

09:07.133 --> 09:08.732
Happy New Year, everyone.

09:08.732 --> 09:09.852
Happy New Year.

09:09.852 --> 09:11.813
Happy New Year, everyone.

09:11.813 --> 09:13.596
Happy New Year, everyone.

09:14.120 --> 09:15.773
Happy New Year.

09:15.773 --> 09:18.153
Happy New Year.

09:18.924 --> 09:19.528
(Happy New Year.)

09:19.528 --> 09:20.200
(Happy New Year.)

09:20.200 --> 09:21.000
(Happy New Year.)

09:21.000 --> 09:23.548
(1 message from Qiang Qingci. Friends)

09:26.933 --> 09:29.192
(Qiang Qingci)
(I gotta go now.)

09:30.692 --> 09:32.232
(Shengshengman)
(OK.)

09:35.372 --> 09:38.153
(Qiang Qingci)
(Can I add you on WeChat?)

09:45.852 --> 09:48.393
(Moqingcheng,
this is my ID. I gotta go.)

09:52.487 --> 09:55.339
(Moqingcheng,
this is my ID. I gotta go.)

09:55.492 --> 10:01.033
Mo, Mo, Mo Qingcheng.

10:03.653 --> 10:05.872
(Search for Moqingcheng)
Qingcheng.

10:10.572 --> 10:11.272
(Moqingcheng, China)

10:11.272 --> 10:13.056
(Qiang Qingci)

10:16.940 --> 10:19.292
(I accepted your request.
We can start chatting now.)

10:21.868 --> 10:24.668
(I accepted your request.
We can start chatting now.)

10:28.452 --> 10:32.188
(Mr. Qiang Qingci,
this is Shengshengman.)

10:32.972 --> 10:34.844
(Typing...)

10:50.372 --> 10:51.753
I know.

10:52.572 --> 10:54.513
(What should I say?)

11:04.653 --> 11:05.673
What?

11:10.612 --> 11:12.732
Well,

11:13.320 --> 11:16.192
what can I do for you, Mr. Qiang?

11:17.773 --> 11:20.313
(Is it too formal?)

11:20.893 --> 11:22.184
Nothing much.

11:22.184 --> 11:24.393
I remember you owe me a song.

11:27.133 --> 11:28.872
You want to hear it now?

11:34.212 --> 11:35.433
Now?

11:42.813 --> 11:44.832
No, what I meant was...

11:49.773 --> 11:52.072
It's too late now. Tomorrow, okay?

11:53.852 --> 11:55.712
(He must be busy.)

12:00.452 --> 12:03.313
Let me find a song.

12:09.772 --> 12:11.484
(Hold to talk)

12:11.653 --> 12:13.712
(He left so many voice messages.)

12:21.933 --> 12:24.952
It's been so long
since I last told you a recipe.

12:26.133 --> 12:28.112
Black pepper stir-fried ribs.

12:29.253 --> 12:30.712
It is really good.

12:31.452 --> 12:34.952
Use baby beef ribs.

12:40.173 --> 12:43.913
Debone the ribs.
Add crushed black pepper,

12:44.413 --> 12:47.472
black pepper sauce and rice wine.

12:49.653 --> 12:52.540
Then add oil and stir-fry on high heat

12:53.173 --> 12:55.232
until the meat changes color.

12:56.933 --> 13:00.793
Then add green onions,
winter bamboo shoots and colored pepper.

13:02.053 --> 13:05.564
Stir-fry on high heat until cooked
and then it's finished.

13:06.184 --> 13:10.372
Black pepper brings
a rich barbecue flavor. It's very nice.

13:10.372 --> 13:15.212
If you don't want baby beef ribs,
you can use beef loin.

13:15.212 --> 13:17.872
But baby beef ribs are more suitable.

13:18.492 --> 13:23.513
Okay, it's very late.
Go to bed early. Good night.

13:27.173 --> 13:30.352
Good night, Mr. Qiang Qingci.

14:06.252 --> 14:08.636
(Moqingcheng, China)

14:17.972 --> 14:21.013
No wonder the kitchen light is on.

14:21.013 --> 14:22.372
What are you doing?

14:22.372 --> 14:25.692
I-I-I'm hungry,
so I'm here for some cereal.

14:25.692 --> 14:27.413
Mom, why are you still up?

14:27.413 --> 14:28.972
I lay down,

14:28.972 --> 14:32.433
but I remembered
the kitchen window was not closed.

14:35.293 --> 14:37.992
Don't forget
to turn off the light later.

14:47.980 --> 14:49.452
(Send a post)

14:49.452 --> 14:51.653
(I'm so happy. What should I do?)

14:51.653 --> 14:53.393
(I'm really happy.)

15:08.396 --> 15:10.229
(218 comments)

15:10.253 --> 15:13.153
Why are there suddenly so many comments?

15:14.604 --> 15:17.084
(I didn't see anything.)

15:21.000 --> 15:23.644
(I didn't see anything.)

15:26.028 --> 15:28.096
(Perfect Voice_Qiang Qingci:
Glad to see it.)

15:31.893 --> 15:32.852
Happy New Year.

15:32.852 --> 15:34.173
Happy New Year.

15:34.173 --> 15:35.692
Where are you going?

15:35.692 --> 15:36.893
To visit his granny.

15:36.893 --> 15:37.933
New Year's visit.

15:37.933 --> 15:38.533
Me too.

15:38.533 --> 15:39.913
Happy New Year.

15:45.653 --> 15:47.753
Sheng, wake up now.

15:49.413 --> 15:51.753
Let me sleep a little longer, grandpa.

15:52.732 --> 15:54.673
Your friend is here.

15:55.212 --> 15:56.773
Don't lie to me.

15:56.773 --> 15:59.232
They've all gone home for the festival.

15:59.972 --> 16:02.332
Get up early to eat tasty food.

16:02.332 --> 16:04.793
My mom made meat zongzi for you.

16:06.053 --> 16:07.433
I'm coming.

16:10.732 --> 16:12.372
Why did you all come?

16:12.372 --> 16:14.053
- Happy New Year.
- Happy New Year.

16:14.053 --> 16:15.692
Happy New Year.

16:15.692 --> 16:16.732
And zongzi?

16:16.732 --> 16:18.076
Here.

16:19.133 --> 16:21.413
Don't rush. We have a surprise for you.

16:21.413 --> 16:22.372
What surprise?

16:22.372 --> 16:24.893
Change your clothes
and follow us. You'll see then.

16:24.893 --> 16:26.053
Where are we going?

16:26.053 --> 16:28.284
Change your clothes. You'll know.

16:28.852 --> 16:30.513
Just around the corner.

16:32.492 --> 16:35.053
Look, it's that yellow house.

16:35.053 --> 16:36.933
Quiet in the bustle. Pretty, right?

16:36.933 --> 16:38.893
Where are you taking me?

16:38.893 --> 16:40.692
You'll know when we get there.

16:40.692 --> 16:41.832
It's here.

16:46.372 --> 16:47.772
Come in.

16:54.060 --> 16:56.636
(Zhaozhaomumu Music Studio)

17:00.332 --> 17:01.412
This...

17:01.412 --> 17:03.632
Oh, my God.

17:06.773 --> 17:08.172
When did you prepare this?

17:08.172 --> 17:09.493
Why didn't I know at all?

17:09.493 --> 17:11.172
Leader asked for secrecy.

17:11.172 --> 17:13.352
It's a surprise for you.

17:15.253 --> 17:17.193
There's a countertop here.

17:20.773 --> 17:22.513
And a kitchen.

17:23.973 --> 17:27.092
What's that? It's so cute.

17:27.092 --> 17:29.013
The former tenant ran a kids' art class.

17:29.013 --> 17:31.432
I thought it was cute, so I kept it.

17:33.852 --> 17:36.132
Isn't this our work display wall?

17:36.132 --> 17:38.440
(Pine Song, Dim Clouds and Snowy Plain)
Only two now, though.

17:40.493 --> 17:43.193
What's that room over there?

17:47.500 --> 17:50.080
(Fortune)

18:09.420 --> 18:12.128
(Guai)

18:14.092 --> 18:15.233
This...

18:17.092 --> 18:18.152
This...

18:18.852 --> 18:20.912
Are they really ours?

18:22.132 --> 18:23.313
Happy?

18:24.253 --> 18:25.753
Very much so.

18:27.253 --> 18:30.632
How about we perform together
to check it out?

18:31.773 --> 18:32.813
Sure.

18:32.813 --> 18:33.912
Come on.

19:12.773 --> 19:15.193
It's a pity I didn't bring my flute.

19:21.213 --> 19:23.213
I bought it with the money I made.

19:23.213 --> 19:25.932
I'll pay you back.
It's not easy for you to make money.

19:25.932 --> 19:28.033
You bought me a mic last year.

19:35.948 --> 19:37.404
(Guai)

20:05.412 --> 20:06.572
(This is my club.)

20:06.572 --> 20:08.932
(Zhaozhaomumu.
It's been around for two years.)

20:08.932 --> 20:10.313
(There's only four of us.)

20:11.132 --> 20:13.652
(She is Leader, )

20:13.652 --> 20:15.693
(responsible for post-production,
art design and publicity.)

20:15.693 --> 20:18.112
(She is also our lead singer.)

20:19.172 --> 20:21.572
(He's Off Key,
Head of the Lyrics Department.)

20:21.572 --> 20:22.733
(Our lyricist.)

20:22.733 --> 20:25.592
(But he is the only one
in his department.)

20:30.652 --> 20:31.612
(This is Guai.)

20:31.612 --> 20:33.852
(Guai and I compose and arrange music.)

20:33.852 --> 20:35.092
(We are also singers.)

20:35.092 --> 20:38.892
(Our vocal department is the largest
and has the most members.)

20:38.892 --> 20:42.753
(We don't have to rent others' studios
for recording anymore.)

21:03.372 --> 21:07.313
Rumor has it that Sheng
is involved in a relationship.

21:09.453 --> 21:12.764
The one known to the whole world.

21:13.352 --> 21:15.313
That guy of the Perfect Voice Studio.

21:17.813 --> 21:21.332
It's just because my roommate
cooperated with the studio.

21:21.332 --> 21:24.252
I happened to be a music director,
so I knew him.

21:24.892 --> 21:27.332
Alright, we're not clueless

21:27.332 --> 21:28.572
(Zhaozhaomumu)
about who you know.

21:28.572 --> 21:31.693
We were all shocked
when we first heard it.

21:31.693 --> 21:34.053
Others say you're riding his coattails.

21:34.053 --> 21:36.493
Latching onto Qiang Qingci
through the anniversary event.

21:36.493 --> 21:37.733
It makes me so angry.

21:37.733 --> 21:40.372
Yes, so many people are envious.

21:40.372 --> 21:42.553
Their words are so harsh.

21:46.213 --> 21:48.053
Okay, it's the Spring Festival.

21:48.053 --> 21:49.872
Don't let them upset you.

21:50.372 --> 21:52.072
It's okay. I'm fine.

22:05.652 --> 22:09.493
(Everyone misunderstands it.
It will definitely affect him.)

22:09.493 --> 22:12.632
(Should I make it clear to him?)

22:15.932 --> 22:18.793
I want to tell you something.

22:24.748 --> 22:26.656
(WeChat, Sheng)

22:33.053 --> 22:35.293
(How should I put it?)

22:35.293 --> 22:38.332
(Even though I'm your die-hard fan, )

22:38.332 --> 22:41.033
(I definitely don't have
improper thoughts.)

22:41.572 --> 22:43.553
(This is too direct.)

22:45.013 --> 22:47.932
(Or maybe I give a subtle hint.)

22:47.932 --> 22:50.780
(It was official business.
Don't overthink it.)

22:51.412 --> 22:53.313
(Not suitable.)

22:54.372 --> 22:55.892
(Hold to talk)
(One second?)

22:55.892 --> 22:59.273
(In one second, he could say
two or three words?)

23:01.372 --> 23:02.473
Um.

23:15.733 --> 23:16.832
Um.

23:25.733 --> 23:29.432
Were you sleeping just now?

23:31.813 --> 23:32.912
Um.

23:35.652 --> 23:37.352
(One second again.)

23:44.973 --> 23:46.072
Um.

23:54.652 --> 23:57.553
So, have you woken up now?

24:01.132 --> 24:02.233
Um.

24:08.813 --> 24:11.912
Can I talk about something now?

24:15.652 --> 24:16.753
Um.

24:25.493 --> 24:28.432
(Forget it. I won't say it.)

24:30.733 --> 24:34.832
I forgot what I wanted to say.

24:35.773 --> 24:38.953
You can continue to sleep.

24:56.132 --> 24:58.793
We can just chat about anything.

25:02.604 --> 25:06.204
(Doctors should be benevolent)

25:07.293 --> 25:08.313
Okay.

25:11.293 --> 25:14.392
What should we talk about?

25:18.280 --> 25:19.484
(Moqingcheng)

25:41.572 --> 25:42.892
Hello?

25:42.892 --> 25:44.156
Hello?

25:46.412 --> 25:50.152
Mr. Qiang, are you not busy?

25:51.852 --> 25:53.072
I am resting.

26:03.852 --> 26:07.993
What do you like to do
when you're resting?

26:09.013 --> 26:12.033
Sleep, or go to the recording studio.

26:15.132 --> 26:18.592
(If I were that hardworking,
I would've won all the awards.)

26:22.852 --> 26:24.632
(Why isn't he speaking?)

26:31.813 --> 26:35.912
Are you going
to the recording studio today too?

26:37.612 --> 26:40.672
Is it for game voice acting?

26:43.213 --> 26:45.864
Well...

26:45.864 --> 26:51.313
You haven't attended the anniversary
of the studio for three years.

26:52.773 --> 26:55.273
Why did you attend this year?

26:56.612 --> 26:59.013
It's the 10th anniversary after all.

26:59.013 --> 27:01.592
I had to attend.

27:04.293 --> 27:07.632
It's like an interview.

27:10.453 --> 27:17.672
That's because I really don't know
what you like to talk about.

27:18.733 --> 27:20.693
I've been inactive online for a while.

27:20.693 --> 27:24.053
You can think of me as a friend
that you know in real life.

27:24.053 --> 27:25.912
Just chat about anything.

27:31.892 --> 27:33.273
So,

27:34.332 --> 27:36.112
have you eaten yet?

27:39.652 --> 27:43.912
Yes, this question is quite boring.

27:44.733 --> 27:48.592
It's OK. It's mainly
because we're not familiar enough.

27:56.733 --> 28:00.572
I remember what I wanted to tell you.

28:00.572 --> 28:02.832
No easy feat. Go ahead.

28:10.612 --> 28:12.632
It's okay. You can say it.

28:15.533 --> 28:17.473
It's just that...

28:18.612 --> 28:22.372
Because you helped me get
the chance of the collaborative cover,

28:22.372 --> 28:24.753
some negative rumors

28:26.253 --> 28:28.132
appeared online.

28:28.132 --> 28:31.852
Actually, my initial thoughts
were really simple.

28:31.852 --> 28:33.892
Being able to collaborate with masters

28:33.892 --> 28:36.672
must be every unknown's pursuit.

28:37.453 --> 28:40.604
But now, I'm just worried

28:41.128 --> 28:44.513
that it will have
a negative impact on you.

28:45.973 --> 28:46.993
Like?

28:49.092 --> 28:51.112
Like...

28:52.852 --> 28:54.112
Losing fans.

28:55.453 --> 28:59.273
Lots of gossip.

29:03.733 --> 29:07.672
(He seems so indifferent
as if he doesn't care.)

29:11.733 --> 29:12.793
Come in.

29:15.332 --> 29:17.233
Dr. Mo, please sign here.

29:17.308 --> 29:19.228
(Voice call duration 01:29)
(Someone's asking for me.)

29:45.493 --> 29:48.172
If online comments make you unhappy,

29:48.172 --> 29:51.473
shut the computer off,
and it'll be nothing.

29:52.693 --> 29:54.344
As a dubbing actor,

29:54.344 --> 29:57.172
the most important thing is my work.

29:57.172 --> 30:00.072
Other than that, what others say

30:00.852 --> 30:02.473
doesn't matter.

30:11.652 --> 30:16.352
Sheng, do you owe me something?

30:18.013 --> 30:20.392
Oh, right. I still owe him a song.

30:25.053 --> 30:28.912
I didn't forget. Mr. Qiang,
what do you want to listen to?

30:30.533 --> 30:33.513
I heard from Juemei
you played an instrument.

30:35.412 --> 30:38.293
I learned a bit. I learned the piano
when I was little.

30:38.293 --> 30:41.172
Then I self-studied
the guzheng and the flute,

30:41.172 --> 30:44.132
because I like traditional style music.

30:44.132 --> 30:46.993
Would you like me to sing while playing?

30:49.973 --> 30:51.753
If it's okay for you.

30:53.132 --> 30:58.513
Alright, Mr. Qiang, let me prepare.

30:59.293 --> 31:01.553
Easy. I'll go to the studio.

31:05.733 --> 31:06.993
The computer.

31:22.332 --> 31:23.693
Happy New Year, Dr. Mo.

31:23.693 --> 31:24.832
Happy New Year.

31:30.813 --> 31:32.412
Why the rough act?

31:32.412 --> 31:34.472
- It's hard to get you to treat us.
- Hey.

31:34.472 --> 31:37.244
Will you eat or not? If not, leave.

31:38.013 --> 31:39.612
Mr. Mo is back.

31:39.612 --> 31:40.813
You're finally back.

31:40.813 --> 31:41.932
Come and do me justice.

31:41.932 --> 31:44.932
They made me go grocery shopping
once I got off the plane.

31:44.932 --> 31:47.253
They only talked but didn't do anything.

31:47.253 --> 31:48.892
They can only babble. Look.

31:48.892 --> 31:53.213
Your team asked us to record
during the Chinese New Year.

31:53.213 --> 31:55.293
Shouldn't you treat us?

31:55.293 --> 31:58.892
Isn't my early return
worthy of a hot pot?

31:58.892 --> 32:00.892
It's for Mr. Mo. You think it's for you?

32:00.892 --> 32:01.852
Well said.

32:01.852 --> 32:03.332
Is it OK for you to return?

32:03.332 --> 32:05.733
Yeah. I said I came back early
for a blind date.

32:05.733 --> 32:07.652
You really came up with a good excuse.

32:07.652 --> 32:09.693
What's wrong? What a good excuse.

32:09.693 --> 32:14.033
Especially for an eligible bachelor
of age.

32:16.132 --> 32:18.572
Shut up. Sit and eat together.

32:18.572 --> 32:21.033
- Sit.
- I've got some other things. You eat.

32:22.293 --> 32:23.852
You upset him and he's gone.

32:23.852 --> 32:24.572
Not eating?

32:24.572 --> 32:25.872
You eat first.

32:29.533 --> 32:32.953
I think something's off with Mr. Mo.

32:34.053 --> 32:35.652
Do you even need to mention it?

32:35.652 --> 32:37.852
I can tell from your forehead wrinkles.

32:37.852 --> 32:39.493
Get lost. I don't have them.

32:39.493 --> 32:40.773
Go away.

32:40.773 --> 32:45.193
This time, the long-standing bachelor
is going to be in love.

32:48.932 --> 32:52.412
Love. It's beyond words.

32:52.412 --> 32:54.013
Come on, cheers.

32:54.013 --> 32:55.772
Let's reconcile.

32:56.332 --> 32:57.132
Narrow-minded.

32:57.132 --> 32:58.053
Why didn't you open it?

32:58.053 --> 32:59.213
Reluctant?

32:59.213 --> 33:00.213
A bit insincere.

33:00.213 --> 33:01.233
Geez.

33:18.453 --> 33:19.473
I'm here.

33:20.813 --> 33:23.912
I'm ready too.
Please go to the chatroom.

33:29.372 --> 33:30.172
The number is...

33:30.172 --> 33:31.313
I'm here.

33:31.932 --> 33:34.953
(Qiang Qingci, Shengshengman)
I came last time so I still remember it.

33:40.013 --> 33:43.493
I'll give you admin rights then.

33:43.493 --> 33:45.072
Okay, thanks.

33:51.213 --> 33:52.813
What do you want to listen to?

33:52.813 --> 33:55.513
Whatever you're used to.

33:56.773 --> 34:00.133
Then I'll sing the song
from my club exam.

34:00.133 --> 34:03.093
I sang it while playing the instrument.

34:03.093 --> 34:04.872
I remember the score.

34:05.412 --> 34:07.073
You have a nice voice.

34:08.613 --> 34:10.332
Good for unaccompanied singing.

34:12.372 --> 34:13.948
Then I'll start now.

34:14.452 --> 34:15.580
Okay.

34:30.412 --> 34:33.032
Sorry, I'm sorry. I'll restart.

34:35.813 --> 34:39.233
No problem. The prelude sounded good.

35:04.892 --> 35:07.613
♪ Oh, crescent moon ♪

35:07.613 --> 35:12.313
♪ Pulling a wisp of a cloud
to whisper goodnight ♪

35:13.693 --> 35:17.733
♪ The tip of the pen
outlines the deep and shallow ♪

35:17.733 --> 35:23.193
♪ Writing the name
a thousand times while murmuring it ♪

35:25.293 --> 35:28.093
♪ Don't blink, evening wind ♪

35:28.093 --> 35:33.113
♪ Please carry my silent thoughts ♪

35:34.253 --> 35:38.293
♪ Hidden in dreams ♪

35:38.293 --> 35:43.593
♪ Entangled between the words
of the years ♪

35:45.892 --> 35:51.133
♪ So many days and nights
were filled with my lingering longing ♪

35:51.133 --> 35:56.253
♪ And all I got was a fleeting glimpse ♪

35:56.253 --> 35:59.213
♪ Kept in my heart ♪

35:59.213 --> 36:04.372
♪ And for whom does it linger again ♪

36:04.372 --> 36:09.532
♪ From now on, the moon in my heart
forever hangs high for you ♪

36:09.532 --> 36:14.492
♪ Reading through the pages of the past
but refusing to say goodbye ♪

36:14.492 --> 36:16.972
♪ The pictures in my memory ♪

36:16.972 --> 36:19.693
♪ Collect the past ♪

36:19.693 --> 36:23.273
♪ As if it were yesterday ♪

36:24.613 --> 36:27.932
Our music director is really talented.

36:27.932 --> 36:32.093
(Doudoubing)
Yes, her casual humming is wonderful.

36:32.093 --> 36:34.012
It is pure and natural.

36:34.012 --> 36:36.173
No wonder Qiang Qingci likes it.

36:36.173 --> 36:38.573
Mr. Qiang Qingci, Miss Shengshengman,

36:38.573 --> 36:41.052
(Feng Yasong)
sorry to interrupt your date.

36:41.052 --> 36:42.133
(When did they come?)

36:42.133 --> 36:43.972
- Doudoubing asked me here.
- Feishao asked me here.

36:43.972 --> 36:45.173
Wang Ke called me over.

36:45.173 --> 36:46.253
I'm having hot pot with Juemei.

36:46.253 --> 36:48.720
I'm chatting with Geng Xiaoxing.

36:48.744 --> 36:51.036
(Geng Xiaoxing entered)
I came in by chance.

36:51.892 --> 36:55.693
(Feishao)
Sheng, Mr. Qiang is quite selfish,

36:55.693 --> 36:58.052
continuously kicking us out.

36:58.052 --> 36:59.892
We only heard in bits and pieces.

36:59.892 --> 37:02.052
Exactly, it's like a seesaw battle.

37:02.052 --> 37:03.452
He kicked, and we entered.

37:03.452 --> 37:07.992
We just want to see how he...?

37:09.852 --> 37:10.760
Actually, I...

37:10.760 --> 37:13.692
I made a bet with Sheng. She lost,

37:14.248 --> 37:16.773
so she had to sing a few songs for me.

37:16.773 --> 37:22.173
(Did I? But this seems
to be the most reasonable excuse.)

37:22.173 --> 37:24.412
How could I be missing from a bet?

37:24.412 --> 37:26.052
I'm your die-hard fan.

37:26.052 --> 37:28.012
You'd better stop.

37:28.012 --> 37:31.012
Every time Linglong produces a new song,

37:31.012 --> 37:33.653
she lets Mr. Qiang listen to it.

37:33.653 --> 37:37.912
Does our Mr. Qiang
still need songs to listen to?

37:41.012 --> 37:43.412
(So, Linglong is pursuing Qiang Qingci.)

37:43.412 --> 37:45.613
Linglong has a mature lady's voice.

37:45.613 --> 37:47.332
Qiang definitely isn't into that.

37:47.332 --> 37:50.293
Otherwise, they would have been together
for so many years.

37:50.293 --> 37:51.752
(I guess so.)

37:51.752 --> 37:55.213
Our Qiang is done now.

37:55.213 --> 37:56.273
Coming.

37:56.852 --> 37:58.412
The meat's gone.

37:58.412 --> 37:59.332
I'll go get some.

37:59.332 --> 38:00.992
I'll just eat veggies.

38:01.813 --> 38:03.293
There are shrimps in the fridge.

38:03.293 --> 38:04.932
Okay, I'll get it.

38:04.932 --> 38:05.773
Season it.

38:05.773 --> 38:07.813
Here, coriander and green onions.

38:07.813 --> 38:09.052
Alright.

38:09.932 --> 38:13.673
Here come the shrimps.
I brought you a drink.

38:14.492 --> 38:16.912
Welcome to our hot pot party.

38:18.093 --> 38:19.472
Mo has something.

38:20.972 --> 38:22.268
Wang Ke,

38:22.792 --> 38:24.156
there's bird flu.

38:24.733 --> 38:27.644
Mr. Mo, don't scare me.

38:28.213 --> 38:32.173
You guys are too much. There are still
three women here who haven't eaten yet.

38:32.173 --> 38:36.372
Doudou, Mr. Mo can be
quite scary when he's hungry.

38:36.372 --> 38:39.173
I suggest you wait
until he's finished eating.

38:39.173 --> 38:40.316
Alright.

38:41.733 --> 38:42.932
Weibo.

38:42.932 --> 38:43.452
Look.

38:43.452 --> 38:44.613
What's going on?

38:44.613 --> 38:46.213
Nothing other than gossip

38:46.213 --> 38:48.213
can make Doudou so excited. Hurry.

38:48.213 --> 38:50.392
Sheng, Weibo, look at Weibo.

38:52.588 --> 38:54.428
(2103 messages)

39:03.693 --> 39:07.133
(It's confirmed?)
(If Mr. Qiang reposts and reveals)

39:07.133 --> 39:09.032
(his favorite voice,
I'll give a box of Haoshi chocolate)

39:09.032 --> 39:11.213
(to everyone who leaves a comment below.)

39:11.213 --> 39:12.273
(Pay now.)

39:21.253 --> 39:22.412
He is gonna be broke.

39:22.412 --> 39:24.012
Sure.

39:24.012 --> 39:27.593
With your repost, Shengshengman
became popular in no time.

39:30.133 --> 39:32.813
Sheng, go and cover for your cousin.

39:32.813 --> 39:34.253
He'll be late for his date.

39:34.253 --> 39:36.293
Your dad and I
will go to the supermarket.

39:36.293 --> 39:37.813
Come home later for lunch.

39:37.813 --> 39:38.992
Okay.

39:41.932 --> 39:44.633
Sheng, you lost the connection?

39:46.653 --> 39:49.852
Sorry, I have an urgent matter.
I need to go.

39:49.852 --> 39:52.372
See you next time. Bye.

39:52.372 --> 39:55.173
Oh, no. Is she scared?

39:55.173 --> 39:56.793
It scared her away.

40:03.332 --> 40:05.532
Hurry up. Your cousin is in a hurry.

40:05.532 --> 40:09.133
By the way, the girl
who just arrived today is new here.

40:09.133 --> 40:10.173
Take care of her.

40:10.173 --> 40:11.233
Got it.

40:26.332 --> 40:27.892
(What's the big deal?)

40:27.892 --> 40:29.412
(Truly nothing.)

40:29.412 --> 40:32.372
(That kind of joke
is very common online.)

40:32.372 --> 40:35.693
(Moreover, he just said
he liked my voice.)

40:35.693 --> 40:37.313
(It's nothing.)

40:41.932 --> 40:45.532
(But he made
such a heartfelt recommendation.)

40:45.532 --> 40:47.972
(I need to express some gratitude.)

40:47.972 --> 40:50.613
(After all, his posting
one recommendation)

40:50.613 --> 40:53.352
(is more effective than my cover songs.)

41:11.852 --> 41:14.932
(Thank you for your recommendation.)

41:14.932 --> 41:16.432
Who is that?

41:19.613 --> 41:20.633
Who?

41:22.133 --> 41:24.613
Not at all. I am currently eating.

41:24.613 --> 41:27.952
It's inconvenient for me to type.
How about voice chat?

41:29.372 --> 41:30.392
Okay.

41:31.653 --> 41:35.552
So, do you still owe me a few songs?

41:37.733 --> 41:41.872
If you're not tired of it,
I'll sing for you anytime.

41:43.892 --> 41:47.352
He's smiling.

41:48.573 --> 41:50.133
Too low. I can't hear it.

41:50.133 --> 41:50.773
Look.

41:50.773 --> 41:52.713
You're not home.

41:54.813 --> 41:57.073
No, I'm about to ride somewhere.

41:59.052 --> 41:59.932
Riding.

41:59.932 --> 42:02.832
Okay. Let's not talk for now. Be safe.

42:05.452 --> 42:07.032
Alright, goodbye.

42:20.293 --> 42:22.173
I'm becoming increasingly curious

42:22.173 --> 42:25.532
about Shengshengman's look.

42:25.532 --> 42:27.613
Juemei, have you ever seen her?

42:27.613 --> 42:29.352
I didn't have a chance.

42:30.613 --> 42:32.932
Mr. Mo, didn't you
always avoid interacting

42:32.932 --> 42:36.012
with strangers on Weibo?

42:36.012 --> 42:38.552
Her voice is nice, so I recommended her.

42:40.133 --> 42:41.133
Indeed, it is nice.

42:41.133 --> 42:43.412
Understood. You cherish talents.

42:43.412 --> 42:45.012
We trust you.

42:45.012 --> 42:46.332
Yes.

42:48.613 --> 42:49.613
Eat a shrimp.

42:49.613 --> 42:50.332
I cooked one for you.

42:50.332 --> 42:51.813
I forgot about it.

42:51.813 --> 42:53.273
Put it in.

43:04.253 --> 43:05.892
Jia.

43:05.892 --> 43:07.892
My good cousin, if you came later,

43:07.892 --> 43:09.992
I'd get roasted by my buddies.

43:11.173 --> 43:13.372
I knew you weren't going
on a blind date.

43:13.372 --> 43:14.753
Team battle.

43:17.100 --> 43:17.813
(Wangjia Supermarket)

43:17.813 --> 43:18.532
Bye.

43:18.532 --> 43:19.793
Bye.

43:26.492 --> 43:27.673
Hello.

43:28.532 --> 43:31.932
Hello, I am Gu Sheng.
You can call me Sheng.

43:31.932 --> 43:33.693
I know you, Gu Jia's cousin.

43:33.693 --> 43:34.972
My name is Dong Yiru.

43:34.972 --> 43:36.813
Today is my first day at work here.

43:36.813 --> 43:40.213
If there's anything I fall short on,
please point it out.

43:40.213 --> 43:42.532
No, it's quite good.

43:42.532 --> 43:44.972
I'll get back to work then.

43:44.972 --> 43:46.332
Alright, thank you.

43:46.332 --> 43:48.193
Don't. It's my job.

44:06.693 --> 44:08.352
Did you check Weibo?

44:09.573 --> 44:12.332
I am about to cry. Do you know that?

44:12.332 --> 44:14.052
My idol just revealed on Weibo

44:14.052 --> 44:16.872
his favorite voice 20 minutes ago.

44:34.892 --> 44:36.520
♪ I traveled all over the world ♪

44:36.520 --> 44:40.444
♪ Only a song
of the chaotic world was heard ♪

44:41.388 --> 44:43.656
♪ I strip off the bleak armor ♪

44:43.656 --> 44:49.052
♪ But my courage cannot be shed ♪

44:49.678 --> 44:51.880
♪ The wine in the cup is still warm ♪

44:51.880 --> 44:56.316
♪ I can't wait
for the old year's passengers ♪

44:56.904 --> 44:58.728
♪ They were buried in a foreign land ♪

44:58.728 --> 45:04.316
♪ Who remembers the remaining stories ♪

45:04.940 --> 45:06.568
♪ Clouds and moon accompany me ♪

45:06.568 --> 45:08.744
♪ I ride a horse back into the desert ♪

45:08.744 --> 45:10.184
♪ A long spear pokes through ♪

45:10.184 --> 45:12.584
♪ What does fate matter ♪

45:12.584 --> 45:14.152
♪ If love and hatred can't be avoided ♪

45:14.152 --> 45:19.112
♪ Under the flying sand lie the bones ♪

45:19.112 --> 45:20.040
♪ I am destined ♪

45:20.040 --> 45:21.736
♪ To be a bloodthirsty warrior ♪

45:21.736 --> 45:23.976
♪ Only one survives in victory ♪

45:23.976 --> 45:27.016
♪ Raise my eyebrows
and sweep away all doubts ♪

45:27.016 --> 45:27.848
♪ It's worth ♪

45:27.848 --> 45:29.480
♪ My youth's love for hardships ♪

45:29.480 --> 45:31.496
♪ I am invincible and lonely ♪

45:31.496 --> 45:34.792
♪ Who can outshine me ♪

45:34.792 --> 45:38.632
♪ Ancient landscapes feel like
it was just yesterday ♪

45:38.632 --> 45:42.600
♪ Who has passed by in this dream ♪

45:42.600 --> 45:44.648
♪ This tarnished iron armor ♪

45:44.648 --> 45:49.544
♪ Has been hidden in legends ♪

45:49.544 --> 45:50.792
♪ I am destined ♪

45:50.792 --> 45:52.264
♪ To be a bloodthirsty warrior ♪

45:52.264 --> 45:54.312
♪ Only one survives in victory ♪

45:54.312 --> 45:57.256
♪ Raise my eyebrows
and sweep away all doubts ♪

45:57.256 --> 45:59.912
♪ It's worth my youth's love
for hardships ♪

45:59.912 --> 46:02.056
♪ I am invincible and lonely ♪

46:02.056 --> 46:05.192
♪ Who can outshine me ♪

46:05.192 --> 46:09.064
♪ Ancient landscapes feel like
it was just yesterday ♪

46:09.064 --> 46:12.744
♪ Who has passed by in this dream ♪

46:12.744 --> 46:15.144
♪ This tarnished iron armor ♪

46:15.144 --> 46:21.500
♪ Has been hidden in legends ♪

46:30.028 --> 46:31.784
♪ Wars spanning vast distances ♪

46:31.784 --> 46:34.012
♪ Bones to sand ♪

46:34.632 --> 46:35.656
♪ Homeland ♪

46:35.656 --> 46:37.244
♪ Remains unburied ♪

46:37.932 --> 46:39.708
♪ Snow over mountains ♪

46:40.492 --> 46:42.428
♪ Slaughtered and empty ♪

46:42.956 --> 46:45.180
♪ I turn around ♪

46:45.868 --> 46:49.692
♪ But no one returns ♪
